{
  "stem": "26609.18",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was near me, sitting at the beginning, when she got her back from the hospital, you know, was sitting here, and before I fell to prison.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just the first two days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I taught and she listened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I left, the children talk among themselves, hers, the woman's children, Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know where they could-- could get a few books.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe the mother had before, something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she-- she told me later, and I looked in, and I could learn by myself, E, U, O, A, like this, and could hear Polish.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She still can speak a little, but not much Polish, very little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She laughs when I try to talk to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she learned a little Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As she had said, she could hardly read it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was my advertisement in Polish she found in Kassel, where she was with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she saw Wanda Grabowienska.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then she-- she worked out something, that I am alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She couldn't know exactly what it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She ran with-- didn't go to school, ran back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was still undernourished, still sickly, still without hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You have seen it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Not like here, she looks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was years later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Ran back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They lived, a few families in one house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She went to a woman there, an old woman who looked after her, because he was there [? as a ?] police, Jewish police in that-- it was a huge place, so they needed police to get order among the people, they used to-- And that place, there were mostly people who'd survived as partisans, and it was the worst kind of people there.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, I tell you what I lived-- I-- I got through there, through the--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
